works.description: Gorgeous, speedy and sporty are some of the adjectives we can use to describe the range of yachts of varying character from Frauscher. The latest addition to their line of motor yachts is the F 909 Benaco S, which is sure a congenial alternative for a sporting driving pleasure. Its elder sibling, the 909 Benaco, is striking in every way, be it the performance, generous space, first-class design or the fittings.
